1
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,439
Don't think just because His Majesty favors you,

2
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:32,040
you can act without restraint.

3
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,400
If you hadn't reminded me,

4
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,879
I would've forgotten about it.

5
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:38,799
Imperial Inspectorate serves His Majesty.

6
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,599
Since Lord Geng won't let me go,

7
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,480
I'll go ask His Majesty directly.

8
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:44,879
Hold it right there.

9
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,680
Are you threatening me?

10
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,120
My lord,

11
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,879
how would I dare?

12
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,599
Compared to you,

13
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:04,000
I'm absolutely nothing.

14
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,719
We both serve His Majesty, after all.

15
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,319
How about this?

16
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:08,439
Once I return from Zhenyuan County,

17
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,000
all the credit will go to you.

18
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:10,879
And besides,

19
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:15,439
I also have 100 taels to show my respect.

20
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,240
That's bribery.

21
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:30,080
I simply admire your character, my lord.

22
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:31,439
It's just a normal exchange of courtesy.

23
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,039
How could that be considered bribery?

24
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,800
His Majesty truly didn't misjudge you.

25
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,360
Adaptable, upright, and kind.

26
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,879
Willing to stand up for the people.

27
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,840
Imperial Inspectorate needs men like you.

28
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:46,759
This is evidence.

29
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:49,840
You may leave now.

30
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,120
I'll think it over.

31
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,080
Lord Geng must think it over carefully.

32
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,319
The situation is urgent,

33
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:57,360
and the people are suffering greatly.

34
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,319
Get out!

35
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,240
Zhenyuan County belongs to Chongzhou,

36
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,360
the Left Chancellor's fiefdom.

37
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,520
Old Pan,

38
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,159
let's hear it.

39
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,039
What should we do?

40
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,319
Root out the corrupt.

41
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:23,800
Ease His Majesty's burden.

42
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:28,000
It's the Imperial Inspectorate's duty.

43
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,560
You'll lead the team again this time.

44
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,840
It's my duty, without question.

45
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,159
So,

46
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,159
should we bring this kid along?

47
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,000
Ning Chen's status is special.

48
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,080
I'll go ask His Majesty at the palace.

49
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,919
Even if His Majesty agrees,

50
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,520
you must keep him safe.

51
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,360
Old Geng,

52
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,240
Isn't he just the Ning family's bastard?

53
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,479
Is he really that important?

54
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:54,479
I suspect he's His Majesty's bastard.

55
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,039
What did you say?

56
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,599
His Majesty favors him like a prince.

57
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,280
Give it back to him.

58
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,719
If there's a next time,

59
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,840
you'll be punished without mercy.

60
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,479
That little rascal.

61
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,159
Let's go.

62
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,079
Come up and have a chat.

63
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:30,240
Uncle Tianxuan's son.

64
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,000
Isn't that a prince?

65
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,199
What does he want with me?

66
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,399
I'm in a hurry to get to work.

67
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,199
I'll be going now.

68
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,040
Just a few words.

69
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,519
These two siblings...

70
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,759
What are they up to?

71
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,800
Knowing you're heading out,

72
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,759
I came specially to see you.

73
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,480
Here.

74
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,600
My sister prepared this just for you.

75
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,800
They're trying to win me over.

76
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:04,079
Young Master.

77
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,920
I'm not going on a picnic.

78
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:06,720
You!

79
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,240
How dare you!

80
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:09,279
A gift bestowed by this princess,

81
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,199
and you dare refuse?

82
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:12,319
Watch me have you flogged thirty times!

83
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,199
I believe you.

84
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:14,959
Of course I do.

85
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:19,199
So rude.

86
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,560
Ning Chen seems afraid of Huai'an.

87
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,199
Well, if there's nothing else,

88
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,600
I'll take my leave now.

89
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:31,879
Young Master Ning,

90
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:35,519
be very careful in Zhenyuan County.

91
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,920
You're brilliantly talented.

92
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,800
Father wants me to learn from you.

93
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:39,759
When you return,

94
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:42,240
I'll treat you at Zhuangyuan Tower.

95
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,439
Here.

96
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,720
Testing officials with this, are we?

97
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,680
Is this His Majesty's idea,

98
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:53,160
or his?

99
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,160
Young Master,

100
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:59,120
I'm an Imperial Inspectorate Silver Guard.

101
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,920
How could I accept a bribe?

102
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,160
Young Master Ning, you misunderstand.

103
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:06,199
Zhenyuan County is remote.

104
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,279
Unlike the capital.

105
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,240
With some funds for the case,

106
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,959
you can grease the wheels, right?

107
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,800
Well...

108
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:17,319
Is this appropriate?

109
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,560
Of course, of course.

110
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:22,240
If it's appropriate,

111
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,480
then I suppose it's fine.

112
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,279
Taking my goodwill for malice.

113
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:27,800
Very well, then.

114
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,439
Since it's all for the case,

115
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:32,920
I'll respectfully oblige.

116
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,120
I'll be taking off then.

117
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,680
Why do I get the feeling

118
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,519
you don't really like him?

119
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,360
He thinks he's so talented,

120
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,439
and acts so arrogant.

121
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,839
Talks like a stuffy old man, too.

122
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,720
He's just so annoying.

123
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:18,920
Is this woman out of her mind?

124
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,319
What's that supposed to mean?

125
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,600
One team will investigate openly.

126
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,279
The other will go undercover.

127
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,199
Before departure,

128
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,399
everyone prepare accordingly.

129
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,480
This mission

130
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,560
is far from ordinary.

131
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,680
Everyone on this trip

132
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:32,720
must proceed in secret.

133
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,519
Don't hit me, don't hit me!

134
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,439
It's me!

135
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,040
Stop!

136
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,319
You... you...

137
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:39,920
You...

138
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:40,879
You scared me half to death!

139
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,800
A-Are you okay?

140
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,959
You're too brutal!

141
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,160
You hit him till his nose bled!

142
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:45,639
It was just a reflex, I...

143
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,160
You're such a coward.

144
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,040
Why are you looking at me like that?

145
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:56,240
I-I didn't mean to do it!

146
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:57,319
Anyway, pack your things.

147
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:57,959
Pack up!

148
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,360
T-The four of us should head out.

149
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,160
Just the four of us?

150
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:05,399
This time we're going undercover.

151
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:07,040
Too many people will blow our cover.

152
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:07,680
Enough.

153
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,439
You two, go pack your things first.

154
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:11,720
Right, let's go.

155
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,600
This is evidence of your bribery.

156
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:23,360
Keep it safe yourself.

157
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,800
From now on, at the Imperial Inspectorate,

158
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,839
don't pull this stunt.

159
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,600
Hurry up and pack.

160
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,200
What a piece of junk.

161
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,960
Farewell, my lords.

162
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,639
Move out!

163
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,799
Look here.

164
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,559
Zhenyuan County is just ahead.

165
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,759
You two will sneak in disguised later.

166
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:39,799
Ning Chen and I

167
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:41,600
will enter from the front.

168
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:42,559
Got it.

169
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,519
Chen.

170
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,120
What are you doing?

171
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,159
What are you doing?

172
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,080
What's going on with you?

173
00:09:52,159 --> 00:09:52,879
Nothing.

174
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:54,679
I...

175
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,000
Golden Guard Pan.

176
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:57,720
Maybe I should ride with Old Gao

177
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:58,919
and Old Feng instead.

178
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,000
What's that supposed to mean?

179
00:10:00,279 --> 00:10:02,440
I'm not arguing with you, Golden Guard.

180
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,720
It's just...

181
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,240
What? What are you doing?

182
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,000
Golden Guard Pan, no, no.

183
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,039
You don't like men, do you?

184
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,440
I don't like men either.

185
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:09,919
Get lost.

186
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,840
I don't like men either.

187
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,120
But the thing is...

188
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:19,960
the horse...

189
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,440
I can't ride anymore.

190
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,080
If I keep riding like this,

191
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,559
not only will everything get wrecked,

192
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,600
my prostate will be ruined.

193
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,039
Qianlie County? Where's that?

194
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,279
Aren't we headed to Zhenyuan County?

195
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,919
There's no Qianlie County.

196
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,480
Wait...

197
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,360
So you can't even ride a horse?

198
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:39,879
I can.

199
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:42,039
Just a little.

200
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,879
This kid really sucked it up.

201
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:45,480
Didn't say a word the whole way.

202
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,200
Brother,

203
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,200
you're a real man.

204
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,480
Come on.

205
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,759
Let Old Gao take a look at you.

206
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:54,919
See if anything got worn down.

207
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:55,519
No, no, no need.

208
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,279
Really, no need.

209
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:56,759
Old Gao,

210
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:59,399
don't try to take his length

211
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,000
to make up for your shortage.

212
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:01,759
Hey, you...

213
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:02,840
It's all right, brother.

214
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:03,879
If it really got worn off,

215
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,000
we'll send you to the palace as a eunuch.

216
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,159
That works too.

217
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,159
Even if mine got worn off,

218
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:10,360
it'd still be longer than both of yours.

219
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,159
Longer than his, longer than his.

220
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:11,639
Longer than yours too.

221
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,799
Enough, stop bickering.

222
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,039
Since you can't ride,

223
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,279
you three sneak in disguised.

224
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:18,039
I'll go in from the front alone.

225
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,799
Better than dragging dead weight along.

226
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,639
Dead weight?

227
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,639
Golden Guard Pan is wise.

228
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,159
A Zheng,

229
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:27,840
get him some medicine.

230
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,120
Keep a close eye on him.

231
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,039
Got it.

232
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,200
Come on, dead weight.

233
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,279
Let me apply some medicine on you.

234
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:45,799
Old Gao,

235
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,759
With that stance of yours,

236
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:48,639
people might think you were ambushed.

237
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,799
I sense killing intent.

238
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,360
Someone really is attacking.

239
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:54,360
Where's the killing intent?

240
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,240
Right there.

241
00:11:58,679 --> 00:12:00,879
Thirty-six thousand catties.

242
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:05,399
What an extraordinary gift.

243
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:07,600
You flatter me.

244
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:17,399
Damn.

245
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:20,679
Wait, hold on.

246
00:12:21,279 --> 00:12:22,080
Is this really the right path?

247
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:25,600
Li Si described this route himself.

248
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,799
He's a local.

249
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,000
The route shouldn't be wrong.

250
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,840
But there's no way through here.

251
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:31,960
Have you ever heard the saying...

252
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,159
"There were no paths in the world,

253
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,399
but as more people walked,

254
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,080
paths were formed."

255
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,000
Who said that?

256
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:39,799
I did.

257
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,720
Today, I'll set a precedent.

258
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:46,080
And take the road less traveled.

259
00:12:47,679 --> 00:12:48,240
Ning Chen.

260
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:49,519
Stop joking around.

261
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:50,960
These are sheer cliffs.

262
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,679
What, are you going to fly?

263
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,000
Brother, no offense, but...

264
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,639
a cliff this high...

265
00:12:57,039 --> 00:12:58,360
if you happen to fall,

266
00:12:58,919 --> 00:13:00,480
that extraordinary gift of yours

267
00:13:00,759 --> 00:13:01,759
won't be of any use.

268
00:13:05,279 --> 00:13:06,559
Then you two watch closely.

269
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:09,080
It's time to witness a miracle.

270
00:13:10,279 --> 00:13:11,720
You're about to see...

271
00:13:13,519 --> 00:13:15,159
Spider-Man.

272
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,399
Nonsense.

273
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:46,279
So his name is Miracle.

274
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,320
His name is Spider-Man.

275
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,440
Right.

276
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,000
Spider-Man.

277
00:13:52,879 --> 00:13:53,480
Old Gao,

278
00:13:54,879 --> 00:13:57,440
I think I underestimated him.

279
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,080
Thought he was just a pampered noble.

280
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,679
He's got some real skills.

281
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,039
That lean frame of his...

282
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,679
Agile and clean moves.

283
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:09,919
That slim build,

284
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,840
incredibly strong waist,

285
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,679
truly an extraordinary gift.

286
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,080
Ning Chen!

287
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:42,559
Ning Chen! Chen!

288
00:14:45,039 --> 00:14:46,039
